To run this program you need to install some packages like
1) 'pyttsx3' for conversion of text to speech.
2) 'wikipedia' to find solution.
3) 'datetime' to import according to the system.
4) 'os' for operating system
5) 'smtplib' to send basic emails through HTML.
6) 'webbrowser' to search the web.
7) 'speechrecognition' to recognise our speech.
